0 0 moveto
35 rotate
80 0 lineto
stroke
73 0 moveto
73 7 lineto
80 7 lineto
stroke
80 0 moveto
80 80 lineto
stroke
newpath
24 -5 25 0 .2 2 4 arrow
fill
grestore

165.53 145.89 moveto
119.64 145.89 lineto
119.64 211.42 lineto
stroke
126.64 145.89 moveto
126.64 152.89 lineto
119.64 152.89 lineto
stroke
TR (1) 146 184 placeBL
TI (t) 130 106 placeBL
(x) 201 90 placeBL
(y) 90 201 placeBL
TR (\(cos) 170 147 placeBL
2 0 rmoveto
TI (t) show
1 0 rmoveto
TR (, sin) show
2 0 rmoveto
